176 A.3d 213 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. MARJORIE ANNA STUBBLEFIELD, DEFENDANT-RESPONDENT.

C-372 September Term 2017

079586 November 30, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002112-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
